<p>The Sacraments 
The purifying sacraments are seven:</p>
<ul>
  <li>The first one is baptism.</li>
  <li>The second one is strengthening.</li>
  <li>The third one is desert.</li>
  <li>The fourth one is communion</li>
  <li>The fifth one is the cross</li>
  <li>The sixth one is sacramental ordination</li>
  <li>The seventh one is marriage.</li>
</ul>
